snippet.title: Echo Generation - Release Date Trailer (Xbox Game Pass)
snippet.description:
Echo Generation, a turn-based adventure game by Cococucumber, launches on October 21 exclusively on Xbox consoles, Windows PC and Xbox Game Pass on day one! 
https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9nn7m263513g
Discord: https://discord.gg/NZCaCaX27b
